<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>彭博加密货币</title><link>https://bloomberg.com/crypto/</link><description>彭博加密货币</description><lastBuildDate>Thu, 04 Jun 2026 14:30:20 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>战略抛售引发溃败后，比特币与科技股的差距扩大</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-06-03/bitcoin-s-break-with-tech-widens-as-strategy-s-sale-feeds-rout</link><description>在Strategy Inc.出售其庞大加密货币库存的一小部分之后，比特币的抛售一直持续到周三，这扰乱了市场情绪，并扩大了该代币与创纪录的科技股之间的差距。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iaTE4QmyBCK4/v3/1200x-1.png" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 03 Jun 2026 06:25:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-06-03/bitcoin-s-break-with-tech-widens-as-strategy-s-sale-feeds-rout</guid></item><item><title>随着比特币的融化，180％的加密货币反弹显示了新的投资时代</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-06-03/a-180-crypto-rally-shows-new-investing-era-as-bitcoin-stumbles</link><description>随着数十亿美元离开比特币和以太基金，资金正在流入加密货币的一个角落，这承诺了投资者长期以来在数字资产中难以找到的东西：从经济活动到代币价值的更清晰的路径。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iTOFRhQJR_aA/v3/1200x-1.png" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 03 Jun 2026 13:46:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-06-03/a-180-crypto-rally-shows-new-investing-era-as-bitcoin-stumbles</guid></item><item><title>美国制裁伊朗顶级加密货币交易所，持续推动达成协议</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-06-02/us-sanctions-iran-s-top-crypto-exchange-in-ongoing-push-for-deal</link><description>特朗普政府制裁了伊朗最大的加密货币交易所和其他三个实体，以持续努力迫使伊朗伊斯兰共和国达成协议，以结束唐纳德·特朗普总统的战争。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iK6fzGKE5lBI/v1/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 02 Jun 2026 21:22:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-06-02/us-sanctions-iran-s-top-crypto-exchange-in-ongoing-push-for-deal</guid></item><item><title>暴跌后比特币的通胀对冲承诺破灭</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-06-02/bitcoin-s-inflation-hedging-promise-in-tatters-after-36-plunge</link><description>比特币在过去一年中下跌了 36%，本周跌破 70,000 美元，进一步回落，削弱了一些有助于将加密货币带入金融主流的论点。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/ipXriv4u_eVY/v3/1200x-1.png" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 02 Jun 2026 16:09:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-06-02/bitcoin-s-inflation-hedging-promise-in-tatters-after-36-plunge</guid></item><item><title>Polymarket 投注者因 Strategy 的比特币销售而陷入困境</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/newsletters/2026-06-02/polymarket-bettors-struggle-over-strategy-s-bitcoin-sale</link><description>投资者现在实际上正在押注于争端本身。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iGywOI_LYWNg/v9/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 02 Jun 2026 21:00:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/newsletters/2026-06-02/polymarket-bettors-struggle-over-strategy-s-bitcoin-sale</guid></item><item><title>随着比特币跌幅加深，加密货币清算额突破 10 亿美元</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-06-02/bitcoin-tumbles-below-70-000-for-first-time-in-two-months</link><description>比特币情绪恶化在过去 24 小时内引发了近 15 亿美元的加密货币清算，因为最大的数字资产跌至两个月低点。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/i4GS.zfV6DYs/v3/1200x-1.png" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 02 Jun 2026 07:07:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-06-02/bitcoin-tumbles-below-70-000-for-first-time-in-two-months</guid></item></channel></rss>